*Htjela* sam da kupim novu odjeću, ali nemam dovoljno novca. (I wanted to buy new clothes, but I don't have enough money.)

*Htjele* smo da idemo u kino, ali nismo imali vremena. (We wanted to go to the movies, but we didn't have time.)

*Htjelo* se većinom da ode kući. (Most people wanted to go home.)

*Htjela* bih da znam šta će biti dalje. (I would like to know what will happen next.)

*Htjele* su da završe posao što pre. (They wanted to finish the job as soon as possible.)